2005-02-15 11:39  asuraparaju

	* win32/VS2003/: dirac.sln, ConversionUtils/ConversionUtils.vcproj,
	  ConversionUtils/BMPtoRGB/BMPtoRGB.vcproj,
	  ConversionUtils/RGBtoBMP/RGBtoBMP.vcproj,
