	* NEWS: Updated with 0.6.0 release notes.

2006-06-13 12:35  asuraparaju

	* extras/patches/:
	  README_ffmpegsvn_trunk_revision_5470-dirac-0.6.x_patch,
	  ffmpegsvn_trunk_revision_5470-dirac-0.6.x.patch: Dirac 0.6.0
