2004-11-22 14:05  asuraparaju

	* libdirac_common/band_codec.cpp, libdirac_common/band_codec.h,
	  libdirac_common/cmd_line.cpp, libdirac_common/cmd_line.h,
	  libdirac_common/common_types.h,
